          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.The sub-barrier elastic scattering data",
                "gives information about the density at the surface",
                "region, while inner distances are probed through the",
                "data at intermediate energies.The overall systematic",
                "error in the density results is 20-30% arising",
                "from two main sources-the polarization potential and",
                "the shape assumed for the density of the projectile."
              ]
            }
